### ============================================
### BRAND API TESTING
### ============================================
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================
### 1. GET ALL BRANDS (Default pagination)
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/brands
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 2. GET BRANDS WITH PAGINATION
### Page 0, Size 10
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/brands?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 3. SEARCH BRANDS BY NAME
### Search for "Nike"
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/brands?search=Nike
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 4. FILTER BRANDS BY STATUS
### Get only active brands
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/brands?status=active
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 5. SEARCH + FILTER BY STATUS
### Search "Samsung" in active brands only
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/brands?search=Samsung&status=active
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 6. SORT BRANDS BY NAME (Ascending)
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/brands?sortBy=name&sortDir=asc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 7. SORT BRANDS BY CREATED DATE (Descending)
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/brands?sortBy=createdAt&sortDir=desc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

